IT Supports Analyst
Job (IT Job) (Oil and Gas Manufacturing), Cilegon Indonesia
Responsibilities
Monroe Consulting Group is recruiting for a multinational company that has been active in the energy industry for more than 50 years. Our client is an information technology (IT) professional, preferably with a background in manufacturing, to fill the job IT Supports Analyst, to be based in Cilegon, Indonesia. Our client has become a worldwide leader in their industry segment and delivers value to its clients by betting on constant product development, manufacturing excellence and high-quality human resources. The winning candidate will experience a dynamic, stimulating and international environment, allowing them to grow professionally. The company offers good prospects for career progression. Key job responsibilities will include: Provides IT application support across the defined scope (SAP and Local application)Effectively requesting/executing corrective maintenance according to the problem effecting usersEngage in maintenance and evolutions of the applications when requiredResponsibilities may include interacting with key users to document the needs, assess the business critically and priority and collaborate with evaluation of solution alternativesParticipates in system implementation within defined scope: perform system testing, control local suppliers’ execution and collaborate with user trainingParticipates in post-implementation activities to ensure proper communication and the availability of user’s manualsMonitor the system utilization and operation in accordance to what has been established during the project. This also includes monitor the correct operation of interfaces between corporate and local systems. Job Requirements  Bachelor degree majoring in informatics technology (IT) or Computer ScienceMinimum 2 years of IT working experience in metallurgy, oil and gas, heavy equipment or manufacturingMinimum level 1 support experience for SAP FICO, SAP PP and SAP MMExperience in IT-IL process, preferably if have IT-IL certificationUnderstand IT project management and methodologiesAble to work independently or as a teamFluent EnglishWill be based in Cilegon All applications will be treated in the strictest of confidence. If you are a suitable match for this position please send your application to Industrial@monroeconsulting.com
